My Game

About My Game

This game is about catching apple. Everytime he misses the high IQ apple, he will lose 10 percent HP. There are also some low IQ apple. If you hit by that, you will lose certain IQ. When your life become to 0 game is over. Use W to move left and use D to move right.

About Me And My Partner

I am a grade 10 student and my partner is a grade 12 student, we are in the same class at school and we all love to play games. The main designer of the game is my partner and I am focus on webpage. Hope you enjoy it.
